# Cartcrft SPA fallback rules
# Processed by Netlify and Cloudflare Pages (and compatible hosts).
#
# The dashboard is a client-side React SPA mounted at /dashboard.
# Any deep link (e.g. /dashboard/products, /dashboard/orders/123) must
# serve the SPA shell so React Router can handle the route client-side.
# Without this rule, a hard refresh or a direct link to a sub-path returns 404.
#
# Format: source  destination  HTTP-status
#   200 = "serve destination content without redirecting" (rewrite, not redirect)
#   301/302 would break the URL — the browser would show /dashboard/index.html

/dashboard/*  /dashboard/index.html  200
